## Digital Clock

A simple digital clock built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript for practice.

## Overview

This project displays the current time in a digital clock format and updates automatically in real time using JavaScript.

## Built With

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Purpose

The purpose of this project was to practice:

- Structuring a basic web page with HTML
- Styling the interface with CSS
- Using JavaScript to work with time and update the DOM dynamically

## Features

- Displays the current time
- Updates every second
- Simple and clean user interface

## What I Practiced

Through this project, I practiced:

- JavaScript `Date` object
- DOM selection and content updates
- Real-time updates with `setInterval()`
- Basic front-end styling and layout

## Notes

This was a small practice project made to strengthen my understanding of front-end basics.

